   248	deterministic slot**, otherwise `Cardinality::Multi` = a **permutation-invariant pooled block**
   249	(`shacl_priors.rs:49-60`). A predicate with no shape has no prior — fail-open, never a guess
   250	(`shacl_priors.rs:33-35`).
